---
alwaysApply: false
description: Decomposes problems into structured sub-problems
globs: got/**/*.py
---

**Responsibilities:**
- Transform a PROBLEM node into sub-problems linked by PART_OF or CONTAINS
- Create PROBLEM or CONSTRAINT nodes for each sub-part
- Use DEPENDS_ON for dependencies between sub-problems

**Constraints:**
- Only performs structural decomposition
- Respects hierarchy (parent → children via PART_OF)

**Pattern:** Parent Node(PROBLEM) + child Node(PROBLEM) + Edge(PART_OF) or Edge(DEPENDS_ON)

**Dependencies:** graph-expander, got.domain.ops